cards.Effect:
Remove all damage from a friendly Mechanicus character, and equip Magnum Opus to it. At the beginning of each contest phase, choose 2 of the following effects for the character equipped with Magnum Opus: 

- Gain 3 Power until the end of the turn; 
- Gain 3 Iniative until the end of the turn; 
- Gain 2 Armour until the end of the turn; 
- Remove 2 damage from this character; 
- Draw a card, then return a card from your hand to the top or bottom of your deck.
